sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Agent as Strategy Agent
    participant Backend as Backend Services
    participant Executor as PanoramaExecutor
    participant Aero as Aerodrome<br/>(Base)
    participant Moon as Moonwell<br/>(Base)
    participant Avan as Avantis<br/>(Base)

    User->>Agent: "I want to earn yield on $5000 with moderate risk"

    Note over Agent: Strategy Agent analyzes:<br/>- Risk profile: moderate<br/>- Amount: $5000<br/>- Available protocols on Base

    Agent->>Agent: Generate strategy proposal

    Agent-->>User: Strategy Proposal:<br/>1. Swap 50% to WETH ($2500)<br/>2. Supply USDC as collateral on Moonwell<br/>3. Add ETH/USDC liquidity on Aerodrome<br/>4. Stake LP in gauge for AERO rewards

    User->>Agent: "Approve strategy"

    Note over Backend,Avan: Multi-step execution begins

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Backend,Aero: Step 1: Swap USDC -> WETH
        Backend->>Executor: executeSwap(aerodrome, USDC, WETH, 2500, ...)
        Executor->>Aero: Router2.swapExactTokensForTokens(...)
        Aero-->>User: ~0.83 WETH received
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Backend,Moon: Step 2: Supply USDC collateral
        Backend->>Moon: supply(USDC, 2500)
        Moon-->>User: mUSDC minted
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Backend,Aero: Step 3: Add ETH/USDC Liquidity
        Backend->>Executor: executeAddLiquidity(aerodrome, WETH, USDC, ...)
        Executor->>Aero: Router2.addLiquidity(...)
        Aero-->>User: LP tokens received
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 255)
        Note over Backend,Aero: Step 4: Stake LP in Gauge
        Backend->>Executor: executeStake(aerodrome, lpToken, amount, gauge)
        Executor->>Aero: Gauge.deposit(amount, user)
        Aero-->>User: Earning AERO rewards
    end

    Agent-->>User: Strategy executed!<br/>- $2500 USDC collateral on Moonwell<br/>- ETH/USDC LP staked on Aerodrome<br/>- Earning: swap fees + AERO rewards
